flowchart TB
  Cameras[Physical cameras]
  Device[Windows 10 IoT UWP device app\nObserved]
  Backend[Backend registration API\nObserved]
  IoTHub[Azure IoT Hub\nObserved/provisioned]
  Blob[Azure Blob Storage faces\nObserved/provisioned]
  Route[Stream Analytics or route bridge\nDocumented/Inferred, not found]
  ServiceBus[Service Bus queue\nObserved/provisioned, name conflict]
  WebJob[Azure WebJob processor\nObserved]
  FaceAPI[Project Oxford Face API\nObserved/provisioned]
  Emotion[Emotion API\nProvisioned/configured, no observed code use]
  DocDB[DocumentDB\nObserved/provisioned]
  PowerBI[Power BI dashboard\nDocumented only]
  Operator[Operator/initializer\nObserved utility]

  Cameras --> Device
  Device -->|POST /api/device| Backend
  Backend -->|registry management| IoTHub
  Device -->|upload cropped face JPEGs| Blob
  Device -->|device-to-cloud JSON| IoTHub
  IoTHub -. missing implementation .-> Route
  Route -. expected delivery .-> ServiceBus
  ServiceBus -->|ServiceBusTrigger events| WebJob
  WebJob -->|download blob| Blob
  WebJob -->|detect/identify/person/train| FaceAPI
  WebJob -->|events and visits| DocDB
  Emotion -. no observed runtime edge .-> WebJob
  DocDB -. documented dataset unknown .-> PowerBI
  Operator -->|create DB/collections/group/container| DocDB
  Operator --> FaceAPI
  Operator --> Blob
